<p>NOTES: Full company name is Cable Design Technologies Corp.</p>
<p>The company said it recorded non-recurring charges totaling $11.1 million (net of tax) in Q3 1996 in connection with the acquisition of NORDX/CDT Inc., and the related debt refinancing and the common stock offering completed in February 1996.  Excluding non-recurring and extraordinary charges, net income for Q3 1996 and the nine months ended April 30, 1996, would have been $7.2 million ($0.37 per share) and $18.3 million ($1.01 per share), respectively.</p>
